## Limitations

The analysis is based on secondary data and existing literature, which may not capture the most recent developments in global trade dynamics. Additionally, the impact of terrorism can vary significantly across different regions and sectors, making it challenging to generalize findings universally. Further empirical research could provide more nuanced insights into the specific effects of terrorism on global trade.